# Backend Identification Guide:

1) Java: 
   - Check: pom.xml (Maven) or build.gradle (Gradle).
   - Base: maven:3.9-eclipse-temurin-17 (Build) -> eclipse-temurin:17-jre-alpine (Run).

2) Go: 
   - Check: go.mod (shows module name and version).
   - Base: golang:1.21-alpine (Very small footprint).

3) PHP: 
   - Check: composer.json (look for "laravel/framework").
   - Base: php:8.2-fpm-alpine.

4) .NET: 
   - Check: *.csproj file.
   - Base: mcr.microsoft.com/dotnet/sdk:8.0 (Build) -> mcr.microsoft.com/dotnet/aspnet:8.0 (Run).


