# BACKEND FAST-API CONNECTION ISSUE FOUND IN ITS main.py and check paths given

# USE /api/health FIRST - Here's Why:
Endpoint	Purpose	When to use
/api/health	"Is backend alive?" ✅	ALWAYS FIRST - DevOps monitoring
/api/message	Business data	Frontend display - "real app feature"
=====
# 1. HEALTH CHECK (DevOps verification)
curl http://localhost:8000/api/health
# ✅ {"status":"healthy"} = Backend LIVE

# 2. BUSINESS API (Frontend feature)  
curl http://localhost:8000/api/message
# ✅ {"message":"Hello from FastAPI!"} = App WORKING

